{"tid":965574,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"體育局擬邀英超球隊修咸頓來澳比賽😇🇲🇴","createTime":"2019-01-02T07:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T07:11:28.000Z","uid":3014,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ddcdaeacd0d3400a8768a47a786e61d7147fe9","tid":965574,"uid":3014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"(澳門電台消息) 體育局局長潘永權表示，計劃在今年年中舉辦 1項國際足球賽，初步接觸英超球隊修咸頓和內地著名球隊，希望在短時間內能夠公布賽事的安排。<br />\n<br />\n潘永權稱，本澳已很久沒有舉辦國際足球賽，今年適逢澳門特區成立 20周年，希望能夠邀請到外隊來澳參賽。他又表示，澳門將參加今年在澳洲達爾文復辦的亞拉夫樂運動會，計劃將派出青年運動員參加籃球、排球和足球等項目。<br />\n<br />\n潘永權稱，市政署成立之後，體育局已將自由波地交市政署運作，大家將有更好的分工合作，提供更好的康體服務予市民。對於公眾泳池救生員外判服務公開招標的工作，潘永權稱將於稍後展開。 (黃偉昌  黃偉鴻)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>WE THE 修</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ab53c32747720527b92df17cf551d2953ff4cd","tid":965574,"uid":37948,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"請狼隊會唔會易D?"},{"pid":"6f4c498112dc39f213ce9467c11490728f4687d7","tid":965574,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"如果今季降左班咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713ab31f312efc6ad4a3c41c3099c46aaac2b941","tid":965574,"uid":3014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8ab53c32747720527b92df17cf551d2953ff4cd","tid":965574,"uid":37948,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"請狼隊會唔會易D?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"典解貢講"},{"pid":"a51036832d41bc4ec1cb9da3d74cf4556ac42186","tid":965574,"uid":3014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f4c498112dc39f213ce9467c11490728f4687d7","tid":965574,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"如果今季降左班咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"repl